  name=\"default\",\n    tasks=[\n        BuiltIn(\"ensure_worktree\"),\n        BuiltIn(\"set_status\", kwargs={\"to\": \"in-progress\"}),\n        BuiltIn(\"commit\", kwargs={\"message\": \"chore(prd): {prd_id} start work\"}),\n        AgentTask(...),\n        ShellTask(\"test\", ...),\n        ShellTask(\"format\", ...),\n        ShellTask(\"lint\", ...),\n        ShellTask(\"typecheck\", ...),\n        BuiltIn(\"summarize_agent_run\"),\n        BuiltIn(\"commit_transcript\"),\n        BuiltIn(\"set_status\", kwargs={\"to\": \"review\"}),\n        BuiltIn(\"commit\", kwargs={\"message\": \"chore(prd): {prd_id} ready for review\"}),\n        BuiltIn(\"push_branch\"),\n        BuiltIn(\"create_pr\"),\n    ],\n)\n```\n\nAfter:\n```python\nfrom darkfactory.templates_builtin import PRD_IMPLEMENTATION_TEMPLATE\n\nworkflow = PRD_IMPLEMENTATION_TEMPLATE.compose(\n    name=\"default\",\n    description=\"General-purpose PRD implementation workflow.\",\n    applies_to=lambda prd, prds: True,\n    priority=0,\n    middle=[\n        AgentTask(...),\n        ShellTask(\"test\", ...),\n        ShellTask(\"format\", ...),\n        ShellTask(\"lint\", ...),\n        ShellTask(\"typecheck\", ...),\n    ],\n)\n```\n\n### `prd plan` output update\n\nIn the CLI code that displays workflow assignment, check for `workflow.template_name` and append it:\n```\nworkflow: default (template: prd-implementation)\n```\nIf `template_name` is `None`, show `(no template)`.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC-1: `workflows/default/workflow.py` uses `PRD_IMPLEMENTATION_TEMPLATE.compose(...)`.\n- [ ] AC-2: The composed workflow's task list is identical to the previous flat list.\n- [ ] AC-3: `prd plan PRD-X` output shows `workflow: default (template: prd-implementation)`.\n- [ ] AC-4: All existing workflow and loader tests pass without modification.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":